agradables,

1114
01:22:37,440 --> 01:22:39,537
de las desagradables.

1115
01:23:18,720 --> 01:23:21,455
PROHIBIDO
A LAS PERSONAS DE COLOR

1116
01:23:41,840 --> 01:23:43,858
Es Betty Parker.

1117
01:23:44,240 --> 01:23:45,734
Es un ultraje.

1118
01:24:02,879 --> 01:24:04,359
<i>¿Qué demonios crees que haces?</i>

1119
01:24:04,360 --> 01:24:05,614
<i>¡Entra aquí!</i>

1120
01:24:05,840 --> 01:24:06,890
<i>¡Ahora!</i>

1121
01:24:10,520 --> 01:24:14,096
<i>¿Crees que es un juguete?
