1163
01:27:57,760 --> 01:27:59,014
¡Dame el libro!

1164
01:28:06,720 --> 01:28:07,914
Soy yo.

1165
01:28:38,641 --> 01:28:40,293
Vamos dentro.

1166
01:28:56,320 --> 01:28:57,355
¿Hola?

1167
01:29:05,479 --> 01:29:08,499
