se tolerará la música

1204
01:31:10,280 --> 01:31:13,219
que no sea moderada
o agradable."

1205
01:31:14,801 --> 01:31:15,755
"Cinco:

1206
01:31:16,159 --> 01:31:17,115
no habrá

1207
01:31:17,280 --> 01:31:21,679
